des:
Let Alexa suggest you ways to express you love to your loved ones. 
Ask Alexa to love you by saying love me! Quirky and sweet messages for your loved ones!

You can say,
"Alexa, open love me",
"Alexa, start love me",
"Alexa, launch love me"
